### House of Representatives

The [House of Representatives](/United_States_House_of_Representatives), a more immediate reflection of public sentiment, also saw shifts, though the [Democratic Party](/Democratic_Party_(United_States)) still held the reins. During this Congress, two House seats were added for the new state of [Minnesota](/Minnesota), and one House seat was added for the new state of [Oregon](/Oregon), increasing the total membership and further complicating the already tumultuous legislative process.

