*   [Whigs (W)](/Whig_Party_(United_States)): no net change (it should be noted that the Whig Party was in severe decline by this point, with its members having largely migrated to other parties like the Know-Nothings or Republicans)
*   [Republicans (R)](/Republican_Party_(United_States)): no net change
*   [Americans (A)](/Know_Nothing): no net change
